<i>♪ And I shall believe ♪</i>

762
00:46:26,416 --> 00:46:28,541
<i>♪ I'm broken in two ♪</i>

763
00:46:31,500 --> 00:46:34,750
<i>♪ And I know you're onto me ♪</i>

764
00:46:36,541 --> 00:46:39,000
<i>♪ That I only come home ♪</i>

765
00:46:39,083 --> 00:46:41,500
<i>♪ When I'm so all alone ♪</i>

766
