<i>♪ Please say honestly
You won't give up on me ♪</i>

772
00:47:06,083 --> 00:47:08,250
<i>♪ And I shall believe ♪</i>

773
00:47:11,375 --> 00:47:14,250
<i>♪ And I shall believe ♪</i>

774
00:47:16,833 --> 00:47:18,833
<i>♪ Open the door ♪</i>

775
00:47:22,125 --> 00:47:25,208
<i>♪ And show me your face tonight ♪</i>

776
00:47:27,458 --> 00:47:29,625
<i>♪ I know it's true ♪</i>

777
00:47:29,708 --> 00:47:32,083
<i>♪ No one heals me like you ♪</i>

778
00:47:32,666 --> 00:47:35,625
<i>♪ And you hold the key ♪</i>

779
00:47:37,958 --> 00:47:40,708
<i>♪ Never again ♪</i>

780
00:47:43,333 --> 00:47:46,333
<i>♪ Would I turn away from you ♪</i>

781
00:47:48,166 --> 00:47:50,625
<i>♪ I'm so heavy tonight ♪</i>

782
00:47:50,708 --> 00:47:53,458
<i>♪ But your love is all right ♪</i>

783
00:47:54,041 --> 00:47:56,958
<i>♪ And I do believe ♪</i>

784
00:47:59,791 --> 00:48:02,583
<i>♪ That not everything
